OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,FThe UK Government says Wales will now
OL,7,Fhave more say over the Crown Estate,
OL,8,Fwhich owns large amounts of land and
OL,9,Fcoastline here in Wales.
OL,11,FThere'll now be a Commissioner
OL,12,Frepresenting Wales' interests for the
OL,13,Ffirst time, but opponents say the move
OL,14,Fdoesn't go far enough.
