OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,FThe UK Government's Wales Office says
OL,7,Fthe new commissioner will "provide
OL,8,Fadvice at board level on the
OL,9,Fconditions in Wales."
OL,11,FIt says "Their advice will further
OL,12,Fsupport the Commissioners' existing
OL,13,Frole in ensuring Wales benefits from
OL,14,Fthe drive for clean energy, following
OL,15,Fan agreement brokered by the Welsh
OL,16,FSecretary."
