OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,FWelsh Secretary, Jo Stevens, says that
OL,7,F"This is a landmark step toward
OL,8,Fensuring that Welsh prosperity is at
OL,9,Fthe heart of the government's mission
OL,10,Fto become a clean energy superpower.
OL,12,F"Our nation stands to benefit hugely
OL,13,Ffrom investment in floating offshore
OL,14,Fwind and we now have the
OL,15,Frepresentation we need to help seize
OL,16,Fthat moment.
