OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,F"This is a demonstration of how Wales
OL,7,Fbenefits directly from its two
OL,8,Fgovernments working together and I'm
OL,9,Fgrateful to Lord Livermore and The
OL,10,FCrown Estate others for helping to
OL,11,Fmake this happen."
OL,13,FToday's development follows a deal
OL,14,Freached in the House of Lords which is
OL,15,Fdebating a Crown Estates Bill that
OL,16,Fwill now be amended.
