OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,FLord Peter Hain, the former Labour
OL,7,FWelsh Secretary who's amendment will
OL,8,Flead to the change says "I'm really
OL,9,Fpleased that we secured with cross
OL,10,Fparty and Secretary of State for Wales
OL,11,Fsupport the first breakthrough Wales
OL,12,Fhas achieved on having an input into
OL,13,FCrown Office Estate policy.
OL,15,F"This new stance shows that the fresh
OL,16,FEluned Morgan Keir Starmer
OL,17,Frelationship is breaking new ground
OL,18,Ffor further progress on devolution
OL,19,Funder Labour."
