OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru has welcomed the move but
OL,7,Fsays it doesn't go far enough.
OL,9,FThe party's Baroness Carmen Smith says
OL,10,Fthat "Plaid Cymru is glad to support
OL,11,FLord Hain's amendment to the Crown
OL,12,FEstate Bill, which will introduce a
OL,13,Fnew Crown Estate Commissioner to
OL,14,Frepresent Welsh interests.
OL,16,FThis step mirrors the amendment I
OL,17,Ftabled to the same effect at Committee
OL,18,FStage. However, this measure alone
OL,19,Fdoes not go far enough."
OL,26,@rD@FOU{D@XO]
