OL,3,CWales to have more say over Crown
OL,4,CEstate
OL,6,FShe added that, "In Scotland, the
OL,7,FCrown Estate generated #103.6m for the
OL,8,FScottish Government's purse in 2022-23.
OL,10,FThese funds were given to rural and
OL,11,Fdeprived areas in Scotland. Imagine
OL,12,Fhow such a funding structure could
OL,13,Fbenefit communities in Wales.
OL,15,F"The devolution of the Crown Estate is
OL,16,Fcrucial to ensure that income from
OL,17,Fleasing land benefits the people of
OL,18,FWales, as is already the case in
OL,19,FScotland.
